# Project Structure Guide

The application boots from [src/app/gpt-tower/index.js](mdc:src/app/gpt-tower/index.js), which wires the layer pipeline, activation loading, and UI overlays for the GPT-2 tower.

Key building blocks:

* engine/layers/Gpt2Layer.js — per-layer visuals and sequencing.
* animations/ — MHSA, LayerNorm, and vector animation controllers.
* components/ — reusable geometry/visual primitives.
* utils/ — shared constants, colors, trails, and loaders.
* ui/ — DOM overlays and controls driven by `index.html`.

Use this map to quickly jump between the entry point, scene setup, and reusable visualization components.
